    if cutoff_energy < np.mean(cutoff_energies):

        adjusted_cutoff_energy -= (np.mean(cutoff_energies) - cutoff_energy
    
    synthetic_data.append([materials[i % len(materials) if i < len(materials) else 'other',  # Using a placeholder for 'other' to complete the sequence when all materials are used up
